data.description: Charming corner-lot townhome, boasting 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms, all embraced by classic brick architecture. The versatile third bedroom offers the option to serve as an inviting office space, adapting to your needs. The interior features an open dining room for elegant meals, a cozy living room complete with a gas fireplace, and a kitchen that seamlessly connects to the living area and includes a delightful breakfast nook with a great natural light. The primary bedroom is a serene retreat, featuring a spacious walk-in closet, as well as an ensuite bathroom with a walk-in shower, double sinks and built in storage. Step outside to discover a fully fenced yard a with a patio, perfect for you to put your personal touch in creating an ideal space for relaxation and outdoor gatherings. Close tor major highways, this home offers easy access to various dining and shopping options, ensuring a lifestyle of convenience. No rear neighbors means a private back yard to enjoy!  A must see!
